---
name: worker-status
description: Check status of all worker terminals
---

Read and summarize .agent/prompts/_progress.yaml:

1. Show each terminal's current status (monitoring/assigned/completed/blocked)
2. List blocked tasks and their blockers
3. Show completed deliverables by each terminal
4. Suggest next actions for idle workers

Output format:
```
## Worker Status Summary

| Terminal | Role | Status | Current Task |
|----------|------|--------|--------------|
| A | Orchestrator | ... | ... |
| B | Worker | ... | ... |
| C | Worker | ... | ... |
| D | Worker | ... | ... |

### Blocked Tasks
- (none or list)

### Completed This Session
- Terminal-X: {deliverable}

### Suggested Actions
- {idle worker}: {suggestion}
```
